<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;LI BAI (LI PO)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Li Bai is an ancient Chinese poet known for his literary achievements."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-42ffa192b7fac4df845ceaec79fec138</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 1}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUYAB&quot;/&quot;TOKMOK, KYRGYZSTAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Suyab or Tokmok in present-day Kyrgyzstan was the birthplace of Li Bai."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-42ffa192b7fac4df845ceaec79fec138</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CHANGLONG COUNTY&quot;/&quot;MIANZHOU&quot;/&quot;JIANNAN CIRCUIT&quot;/PRESENT-DAY JIANGYOU,&lt;SICHUAN&quot;&gt;">
  <data key="d0">LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A location where Li Bai grew up and studied swordsmanship."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-42ffa192b7fac4df845ceaec79fec138</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;KUANG MOUNTAIN&quot;/&lt;PRESENT-DAY JIANGYOU, SICHUAN&gt;">
  <data key="d0">GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mountain in present-day Jiangyou, Sichuan where Li Bai began his studies at fourteen years old."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-42ffa192b7fac4df845ceaec79fec138</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LI BAI&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Li Bai is a poet who traveled extensively and faced health issues towards the end of life."&lt;SEP&gt;"Li Bai is an iconic poet who lived through various significant events and had interactions with other historical figures."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LADY XU&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Lady Xu was Li Bai's wife, whose death deeply affected him."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;KONG CHAOFU&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Kong Chaofu is one of the recluses who formed a drinking society with others in Yanzhou."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HAN ZHUN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Han Zhun was another member involved in forming a drinking society on Culai Mountain."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MOUNT TAI&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mount Tai is mentioned as one of the locations associated with Li Bai's life and activities."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CULAI MOUNTAIN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Culai Mountain was where a drinking society known as 'Six Idlers of Bamboo Creek' formed."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LI LIN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Li Lin is mentioned in relation to Prince Yong and the An Lushan Rebellion."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DU FU&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Du Fu is mentioned as a poet who met Li Bai, indicating he was also an important historical figure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-af708e7ec8088347425ceeae63f00c9f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BAIDI TOWN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Baidi Town was visited by Li Bai, where he experienced an amnesty that influenced his poetry."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;JIANGLING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Jiangling is a location mentioned in one of the poems written during Baidi Town visit."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MOUNT JINGTING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mount Jingting was revisited by Li Bai, inspiring him to write poetry."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;QUAN ZHAOYI&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Quan Zhaoyi is an old friend of Li Bai who hosted him in Jinling."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DANGTU COUNTY MAGISTRATE'S OFFICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Li Yangbing, a county magistrate at Dangtu where Li Bai sought refuge and passed away."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SPRING 759 AD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Spring 759 AD is a specific year mentioned when Li Bai reached Baidi Town."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;AUTUMN 760 AD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Autumn 760 AD refers to the time period during which Li Bai revisited Mount Jingting and stayed at Quan Zhaoyi's home in Jinling."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-de4bebc2903812b72e0b4c87e9304a1d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WINTER 762 AD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Winter 762 AD is a specific year mentioned when Li Bai died of illness in Dangtu County Magistrate's Office."</data>
